{"tid":733751,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"🇨🇳🇭🇰祖國萬歲！中國獲FIFA表揚","createTime":"2018-07-08T04:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T10:46:50.000Z","uid":20634,"like":5,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"588653d3c62672b7d3c5ac9077a102b5103dac84","tid":733751,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:56:42.000Z","msg":"世界杯八分之一決賽剛剛落下帷幕，四分之一決賽激戰正酣，全球各地的球迷們正享受著足球帶來的盛宴。除了部分球迷能夠去到現場感受之外，絕大多數球迷是通過電視觀看的。中國球迷是其中重要的力量，國際足聯今天就艾特央視體育頻道，實名表揚了一把中國觀眾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/125537_bcb6120d6e2f0512d0ec68eb0097a2b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F125537_bcb6120d6e2f0512d0ec68eb0097a2b6.png&h=19ffb3f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際足聯寫到：「實名表揚這屆觀眾，你們是我見過最棒的一屆！在#FIFA世界杯#1/8決賽期間，以下比賽的收視峰值最令人震驚：法國vs阿根廷，最高觀看人數為54,022,000；巴西vs墨西哥，最高觀看人數為50,518,000；西班牙vs俄羅斯，最高觀看人數為50,229,000。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/125615_709451fad34b28d6bd20719845c3e2a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F125615_709451fad34b28d6bd20719845c3e2a6.png&h=d0911964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從數據可以看到，世界杯的比賽在我國收視率非常可觀，觀眾群體非常龐大。這也能看到觀眾對於足球比賽的喜愛，這還是在國家隊並沒有進入世界杯的數據。若中國進入世界杯，恐怕收視率還會更高。"},{"pid":"4bf1cf7207bda89dc7ba327f2d2deab51b6dd900","tid":733751,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"😂"},{"pid":"f74cf7704e72288a73be7eef372875abe1a4eb64","tid":733751,"uid":28831,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:01:42.000Z","msg":"中國又贏"},{"pid":"132e1e38b40a4694c6a9060e08f812cca0b3aa5a","tid":733751,"uid":24282,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:01:45.000Z","msg":"少人過lol"},{"pid":"bdbf84030d53abe388f1a53eb96b5235970e9e07","tid":733751,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 🇨🇳"},{"pid":"dfaebab77ce1e0f03f29891249ce392004b46fbb","tid":733751,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558f7ca559587085a9db202d27d217701597bae9","tid":733751,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:49:44.000Z","msg":"贏國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cd75c6ab9fd81ca32ef67a8f6a197b4e9b3db5","tid":733751,"uid":5191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:52:55.000Z","msg":"少過tvb收視"},{"pid":"fbaa39fe3923f78d110174c125a3e82e83b75af1","tid":733751,"uid":117509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:55:30.000Z","msg":"講到明為左錢<br />\n下屈黑哨都吹到贏國入決賽周"},{"pid":"4a23e6b8528a3b6fa681a19c52d806a70c52aca3","tid":733751,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T06:00:31.000Z","msg":"14 億人得 5 千萬人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eff22d0b02399278ae833f77255c02f5c3ab264","tid":733751,"uid":59678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a23e6b8528a3b6fa681a19c52d806a70c52aca3","tid":733751,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T06:00:31.000Z","msg":"14 億人得 5 千萬人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T06:05:30.000Z","msg":"因為中國無份踢先得咁少人睇"},{"pid":"7c452315eba1b78aacccf202457faff275ccea26","tid":733751,"uid":38701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbaa39fe3923f78d110174c125a3e82e83b75af1","tid":733751,"uid":117509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:55:30.000Z","msg":"講到明為左錢<br />\n下屈黑哨都吹到贏國入決賽周"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"